Dm_Matrix_Ultimate

This is a death match map and has 36 spawns placed throughout the level.
  The level also contains two teleporters.
  Gravity is set to (0.5) of normal.

This is map 1 of 3 in the Matrix Trilogy. Each map has a different layout and texture set.

Get map 2 of 3, "dm_Matrix_Reload" Here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/108585
Get map 3 of 3,  "dm_Matrix_Revolution" Here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/108588


Blair (Bobpoblo) Burkhardt - Level Design
